description: For the best artisan ice pops on the streets of Indiana, you have to visit Rasta Pops! Inspired by the Brazilian tradition of "picole" vendors, the Santos family is bringing their unique style of frozen treats right to you. With a number of vegan options, a delicious Paleo-friendly pop, and a variety of flavors kids and adults are sure to love, Rasta Pops is sure to have something just for you!
name: Rasta Pops
